    <Content contentid="4635" contenttypeid="LCTN" desc="Location / Locale">
      <Description><![CDATA[<p>Villa Kavaya is located in the scenic village of Pererenan, a part of Canggu that provides an ever-growing number of fashionable new eateries and cool shopping. It is about 45 minutes from Bali’s international airport and a 20-minute drive from Seminyak.&nbsp; The beach – a well-known surfers’ haunt – is just 800 metres down the road.</p>]]></Description>
